.Dd $Mdocdate: April 12 2026 $
.Dt SMTPMIC 4 riscv64
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm smtpmic
.Nd SpacemiT P1 Power Management IC
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "smtpmic* at iic?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the real-time clock in the SpacemiT P1
Power Management IC.
It also provides a way to reset or shutdown some machines that do not
implement this functionality in their firmware.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr iic 4 ,
.Xr intro 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 7.9 .
.Sh AUTHORS
.An -nosplit
The
.Nm
driver was written by
.An Mark Kettenis Aq Mt kettenis@openbsd.org .
